Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.82,0:02:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{Yes. It's delicious, Shirou.}Vâng, ngon lắm Shirou.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.12,0:02:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{I feel like there are more people around today.}Shirou, tôi có cảm giác hôm nay đông đúc hơn bình thường.
