Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.70,0:03:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{Dinner for tonight though will be this.} cái này!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.29,0:03:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'm home.}Em về rồi đây.
