Dialogue: 5,0:03:51.05,0:03:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mừng về nhà!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.59,0:03:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{This kotatsu...}Cái kotatsu này...
